         <listPerson>
            <person xml:id="pers0358">
               <p>Catermole traveled briefly as a helper about <date when="1763">1763</date>, then
                  went to study and assist at Kingswood, while preaching occasionally. He returned
                  to the <seg ana="itinerancy">itinerant</seg> ranks in <date when="1765"
                     >1765</date>, but by <date when="1771">1771</date> it was clear that his
                  temperament did not suit this calling and he settled again. See Atmore, <hi
                     rend="italic">Memorial</hi>, 73; and Pawson, <hi rend="italic">Letters</hi>,
                  3:140.</p>
            </person>
         </listPerson>
      </body>
